I found the complete membership roster.

368
00:20:38,550 --> 00:20:40,090
豪夫和沃尼克都在上面
Hauffe and Wernick are both on it.

369
00:20:40,090 --> 00:20:43,190
我正在对其它成员进行背景追查
I'm running background checks on the other members.

370
00:20:43,190 --> 00:20:45,360
这里  迈克・斯坦根
Here... Michael Stegans--

371
00:20:45,360 --> 00:20:47,230
纳瓦克的建筑包工头
Construction foreman from Newark.

372
00:20:47,230 --> 00:20:49,130
信用记录是从1988年开始
Credit scores only go back to 1988.

373
00:20:49,130 --> 00:20:50,730
如果符合这个模式
If the pattern follows...

374
00:20:50,730 --> 00:20:53,010
那么这个斯坦根就是史戴勒
Then Stegans is really Steiller.

375
00:20:54,570 --> 00:20:57,240
他在布鲁克林有个建筑工地
He's running a construction site in Brooklyn.

376
00:20:57,240 --> 00:20:59,090
我有他的手机
I have a cell phone.

377
00:21:03,250 --> 00:21:04,530
喂
Hello?

378
00:21:06,050 --> 00:21:07,460
史戴勒先生
Mr. Steiller?

379
00:21:09,020 --> 00:21:09,620
不好意思
I'm sorry.

380
00:21:09,620 --> 00:21:12,240
我想你打错了电话了吧
I-I think you have the wrong number.

381
00:21:12,240 --> 00:21:14,410
没时间装了  你给我听好
There's no time for games. You need to listen.

382
00:21:14,970 --> 00:21:16,770
你还记得乌里希・科尔吗
Do you remember Ulrich Kohl?

383
00:21:16,770 --> 00:21:17,800
他还记得你
He remembers you,

384
00:21:17,800 --> 00:21:20,480
就像他记得其他那些史塔西里的同事
Just like he remembered all his old Stasi colleagues.

385
00:21:20,490 --> 00:21:21,970
他去找你了
He's on his way.

386
00:21:23,110 --> 00:21:25,510
你这是在说一个死人
You're speaking of a dead man.

387
00:21:34,190 --> 00:21:36,480
我知道这天迟早会来
I knew this day would come.

388
00:21:37,620 --> 00:21:39,280
你太强了
You were too good.

389
00:21:39,620 --> 00:21:41,220
我是跟最好的人学的
I learned from the best.

390
00:21:41,390 --> 00:21:42,780
跟你学的
I learned from you.

391
00:21:44,530 --> 00:21:46,360
你曾是我的朋友
You were my friend.

392
00:21:47,060 --> 00:21:48,490
你了解我
You knew me.

393
00:21:50,020 --> 00:21:51,580
了解我妻子
You knew my wife.

394
00:21:53,750 --> 00:21:55,700
她跟我一样相信你
She trusted you as much as I did.

395
00:21:55,700 --> 00:21:57,580
你变了  乌里希
You changed, Ulrich.

396
00:21:57,580 --> 00:22:00,270
我看到了那些任务对你的影响
I watched what the missions did to you--

397
00:22:00,470 --> 00:22:02,570
你眼中的黑暗
The darkness in your eyes.

398
00:22:03,830 --> 00:22:05,790
你相信杀人
You believed in the killing.

399
00:22:05,960 --> 00:22:09,820
你训练我  你成就了如今的我
You trained me. You made me what I was.

400
00:22:09,820 --> 00:22:11,790
我深信我的国家
I believed in my country.

401
00:22:11,790 --> 00:22:13,050
深信你
I believed in you.

402
00:22:13,050 --> 00:22:14,830
我们不能救你
We could not save you.

403
00:22:14,830 --> 00:22:17,240
所以你就抛弃安雅和我  将我们留给那些猎犬
So you left Anja and me to the hounds...

404
00:22:17,240 --> 00:22:19,820
就为了纽约的一间公寓和那点钱
For some money and an apartment in New York city?

405
00:22:19,830 --> 00:22:21,520
我不得不收手
I had to get out.

406
00:22:21,520 --> 00:22:24,910
我够强  我生存下来了
I was strong. I survived.

407
00:22:25,120 --> 00:22:27,610
但是他们对安雅的作为  就
What they did to Anja, though...

408
00:22:28,060 --> 00:22:29,650
你必须为此付出代价
You will pay for that.

409
00:22:29,650 --> 00:22:32,760
慢着  慢着  乌里希
Wait. Wait, Ulrich.

410
00:22:34,090 --> 00:22:36,510
