There is something you don't know.

411
00:22:44,680 --> 00:22:46,950
我是唯一一个知道的人
I was the only one who knew.

412
00:22:55,820 --> 00:22:57,320
喂
Hello?

413
00:22:57,590 --> 00:22:58,950
喂
Hello?

414
00:23:08,420 --> 00:23:09,930
安雅还活着
Anja is alive?

415
00:23:10,150 --> 00:23:14,330
我们都叛逃后的几年  她找到了我
She found me a few years after we all defected.

416
00:23:15,640 --> 00:23:19,730
她比任何人都要怕你  乌里希
She was more afraid of you than anyone, Ulrich.

417
00:23:20,610 --> 00:23:21,750
所以  你看
So, you see,

418
00:23:21,750 --> 00:23:26,730
你的复仇根本毫无意义
Your revenge was all for nothing.

419
00:23:56,860 --> 00:23:59,130
芬奇  我们得找出安雅
Finch, we need to find Anja.

420
00:23:59,130 --> 00:24:01,950
我觉得科尔刚刚把她列入了名单
I think Kohl just added her to his list.

421
00:24:05,860 --> 00:24:07,370
车祸是伪造的
The car accident was faked.

422
00:24:07,370 --> 00:24:09,320
她是他的妻子  可她还是背叛了他
She was his wife, and she betrayed him.

423
00:24:09,330 --> 00:24:10,610
对于科尔这样的男人来说
To a man like Kohl,

424
00:24:10,610 --> 00:24:12,880
足够把她列为目标了
That makes her just as much a target.

425
00:24:16,170 --> 00:24:17,240
有个杀手逍遥法外
We got a killer out there,

426
00:24:17,240 --> 00:24:19,190
而我们最好的线索却要被遣返
And our best lead is getting deported.

427
00:24:19,190 --> 00:24:20,780
你不是还有那个孤胆英雄神枪手在找同个人嘛
You still got your vigilante looking for the shooter.

428
00:24:20,780 --> 00:24:21,770
这还不算坏
That's not bad news.

429
00:24:21,770 --> 00:24:24,010
你不能派个杀手去抓另一个  警探
You can't send a killer to catch a killer, Detective.

430
00:24:24,010 --> 00:24:26,020
谁叫那家伙能出成果
Hey, your guy still gets results.

431
00:24:30,140 --> 00:24:32,640
已上路
银色小轿车
牌照 SMH 4642

432
00:24:33,070 --> 00:24:34,920
他们接下来会走小路去机场
They'll take side streets to the airport--

433
00:24:34,920 --> 00:24:35,910
标准章程
Standard procedure.

434
00:24:35,910 --> 00:24:38,310
告诉弗斯科警探把领馆的车载GPS
Tell Detective Fusco to send the GPS tracker number

435
00:24:38,310 --> 00:24:39,890
追踪号码发过来
For the consulate car.

436
00:24:41,420 --> 00:24:42,690
我找到他了
I found their position, Mr. Reese,

437
00:24:42,690 --> 00:24:44,630
但你打算怎么阻止他们
But how do you intend to stop them?

438
00:24:58,390 --> 00:25:00,490
里瑟先生  我表示我现在感到很不自在
Mr. Reese, I'm highly uncomfortable being here.

439
00:25:00,490 --> 00:25:02,190
我表示我现在同感
I'm highly uncomfortable having you here,

440
00:25:02,190 --> 00:25:03,880
但我需要个观察手
But I need a spotter.

441
00:25:18,210 --> 00:25:18,800
报距离
Range it.

442
00:25:18,800 --> 00:25:20,760
不知道  500码
I don't know. 500 yards?

443
00:25:20,940 --> 00:25:22,220
600码
600.

444
00:25:24,910 --> 00:25:26,500
45度斜风
45-degree oblique wind...

445
00:25:26,500 --> 00:25:28,550
四分之三量风速
3/4 value wind speed.

446
00:25:29,170 --> 00:25:30,810
不错啊  芬奇
Very impressive, Finch.

447
00:25:30,820 --> 00:25:32,170
如果你打偏了怎么办
What if you miss?

448
00:25:33,790 --> 00:25:36,440
我可不知道  从没失手过
I wouldn't know. Never have.

449
00:25:47,240 --> 00:25:50,330
停  我们有外交豁免权
Stop. We have diplomatic immunity.

450
00:25:50,330 --> 00:25:53,340
-可我不是外交家  -那你是谁
 - I'm not a diplomat.  - Who are you?

451
00:25:53,340 --> 00:25:56,190
我是那个还有时间去救安雅的人
I'm the guy who still has time to save Anja Kohl.

452
00:25:56,190 --> 00:25:58,830
我知道她还活着  但我要知道她在哪
Now, I know she's alive, but I need to know where.

453
00:25:58,830 --> 00:26:00,360
我们无可奉告
This man has nothing to say.

454
00:26:00,360 --> 00:26:02,430
任何交涉都会违反
Any communication would violate--

455
00:26:02,430 --> 00:26:06,340
我什么都做不了  如果你能就去救她
There's nothing I can do. Save her if you can.

456
00:26:13,960 --> 00:26:16,340
安娜・克莱恩  晨边高地公寓的一个地址
Anna Klein--an address in morningside heights.

457
00:26:16,340 --> 00:26:17,580
是安雅
It's Anja.

458
00:26:44,680 --> 00:26:46,400
安雅不在这  科尔
Anja isn't here, Kohl.

459
00:26:47,310 --> 00:26:48,700
她很安全
She's safe...

460
00:26:48,970 --> 00:26:50,630
在你碰不到的地方
Where you can't get to her.

461
00:26:53,010 --> 00:26:54,610
维洛德手枪哈
That's a Welrod, isn't it?

462
00:26:54,610 --> 00:26:57,170
开火时只有73分贝
Only 73 decibels when fired.

463
00:26:57,170 --> 00:26:59,670
但这阻止不了我近你身
But it won't stop me before I get to you.

464
00:27:00,670 --> 00:27:03,900
我中枪之后极度没耐性
And I lose my patience when I get shot.

465
00:27:08,140 --> 00:27:08,950
安雅在哪
Wo ist Anja?

466
00:27:08,960 --> 00:27:12,010
你打算怎么办  科尔
What's your plan, Kohl, hmm?

467
00:27:12,160 --> 00:27:13,990
你是要把她也杀了
You gonna kill her, too...

468
00:27:14,810 --> 00:27:16,110
你自己的妻子
Your own wife?

469
00:27:16,110 --> 00:27:18,450
你还没计划是不是
You don't have a plan, do you?

470
00:27:22,830 --> 00:27:25,310
你两边的颈动脉
Your external carotid arteries--

471
00:27:25,920 --> 00:27:27,550
要是被阻断
Obstruct both...

472
00:27:30,530 --> 00:27:33,040
你就会带着剧烈的头痛醒来
And you wake up with quite a headache.

473
00:27:34,740 --> 00:27:35,900
乌里希
Ulrich?

474
00:27:35,900 --> 00:27:37,290
不可能
It can't be.

475
00:27:38,960 --> 00:27:40,610
他是来找我的吧
He's coming for me, isn't he?

476
00:27:40,610 --> 00:27:41,840
是的
Yes.

477
00:27:41,840 --> 00:27:44,040
现在最重要的是把你置于警方保护之下
What's important now is getting you into police custody.

478
00:27:44,040 --> 00:27:45,640
第八区有个警探
There's a detective at the eighth precinct--

479
00:27:45,640 --> 00:27:47,240
不  慢着  我们还不能走
No, wait. We can't go yet.

480
00:27:47,240 --> 00:27:48,850
那里很安全  我保证
It's safe there. I promise.

481
00:27:48,850 --> 00:27:51,310
不是现在  求你了  我得打个电话
Not yet, please. I need to make a phone call.

482
00:27:52,780 --> 00:27:54,090
相机
A camera...

483
00:27:57,680 --> 00:27:59,190
真赞
It's extraordinary.

484
00:27:59,860 --> 00:28:02,810
史塔西可会为了这种技术杀人
The Stasi would have killed for this technology.

485
00:28:05,020 --> 00:28:06,620
安雅在哪
Wo ist anja?

486
00:28:09,330 --> 00:28:12,690
人旅行的时候  会学到一些东西
When you travel, you pick up things--

487
00:28:14,050 --> 00:28:15,480
技能
Skills...

488
00:28:15,870 --> 00:28:16,920
物品
Items.

489
00:28:16,920 --> 00:28:17,930
他们都嘲笑我
They all laughed at me

490
00:28:17,930 --> 00:28:20,330
嘲笑我学着用这些针头
When I learned to use these needles.

491
00:28:20,970 --> 00:28:23,010
他们都笑不久
They didn't laugh for long.

492
00:28:23,940 --> 00:28:25,480
我
I was, uh...

493
00:28:26,520 --> 00:28:29,960
在坎大哈时曾被叛军巡逻队绑架走
Bagged by an insurgent patrol when I was in Kandahar.

494
00:28:29,960 --> 00:28:32,300
他们试过电击我
They used electricity on me...

495
00:28:32,300 --> 00:28:34,170
16小时
16 hours.

496
00:28:35,070 --> 00:28:37,130
他们想要的不过是我的名字
All they wanted was my name.

497
00:28:37,130 --> 00:28:39,200
我才不管你名字
I don't care for your name.

498
00:28:40,280 --> 00:28:42,780
尺骨神经是人体内
The ulnar nerve is the largest nerve

499
00:28:42,780 --> 00:28:45,810
没有防护的最大一个神经丛
In the human body that is unprotected.

500
00:28:45,810 --> 00:28:48,760
从肩膀一直通到甲床
It goes from the shoulder, to the fingernail beds,

501
00:28:48,760 --> 00:28:51,480
当经过手肘的时候
When it passes through the elbow,

502
00:28:52,770 --> 00:28:54,760
也就是所谓的"麻骨神经"
It's known as the funny bone.

503
00:28:57,040 --> 00:28:58,870
安雅在哪
Wo ist Anja?

504
00:29:02,230 --> 00:29:04,970
别紧张  我们是自己人
Relax. We're on the same team.

505
00:29:05,380 --> 00:29:09,250
更何况  我这衣服要怎么藏枪啊
And besides, where would I hide a gun in this dress?

506
00:29:09,250 --> 00:29:10,950
你是斯坦顿吧
You're Stanton, right?

507
00:29:11,860 --> 00:29:13,240
这是谁
Who's this?

508
00:29:13,240 --> 00:29:15,010
还没决定呢
Haven't decided yet.

509
00:29:17,130 --> 00:29:18,440
米勒说你们喜欢波本威士忌
Miller said you like bourbon.

510
00:29:18,440 --> 00:29:19,950
你知道他们在这边喝什么吗
You know what they drink here?

511
00:29:20,170 --> 00:29:21,620
李子白兰地
Plum brandy.

512
00:29:22,970 --> 00:29:25,870
-米勒可惜了  -他怎么了
- A shame about Miller. - what happened to him?

513
00:29:26,680 --> 00:29:28,190
没有完成任务
Wasn't getting the job done.

514
00:29:28,190 --> 00:29:29,620
上面发话了
Word came down--

515
00:29:30,060 --> 00:29:31,510
是时候该清理门户了
Time to take the gloves off.

516
00:29:31,510 --> 00:29:35,450
那我们能为你们做什么
So... what can we do for you?

517
00:29:36,830 --> 00:29:39,590
我们在调查关于阿利姆・阿西尔
We're looking into reports that Alim Assir

518
00:29:39,590 --> 00:29:41,270
几周前来到国内的消息
was in country last week,

519
00:29:41,270 --> 00:29:43,500
他也许是来确保他的资金
Possibly to secure financing.

520
00:29:43,500 --> 00:29:44,620
我们上周把所有的情报人员
We sent all of our intel

521
00:29:44,620 --> 00:29:46,290
都派到了中情局
in the pouch to Langley last week.

522
00:29:46,290 --> 00:29:48,350
而阿西尔两天前安然无恙地
and Assir made it out of the country safely

523
00:29:48,360 --> 00:29:49,860
离开了美国
Two days ago.

524
00:29:51,110 --> 00:29:52,470
我们要知道为什么
We want to know how.

525
00:29:52,470 --> 00:29:54,860
我们得到的消息也是
That's also in our intel.

526
00:29:54,990 --> 00:29:58,830
正如我们所说  他肯定贿赂了海关一大笔钱
Like we said, he must have paid customs a fortune.

527
00:29:58,830 --> 00:30:00,880
那他又给了你们多少钱
And how much did he pay you?

528
00:30:05,540 --> 00:30:06,910
开玩笑的啦
Kidding.

529
00:30:07,700 --> 00:30:11,440
我刚也说了  你们哥几个也太紧张了
It's like I said-- you boys are too tense.

530
00:30:12,030 --> 00:30:14,160
该好好放松一下了
Here's to taking the gloves off.

531
00:30:23,060 --> 00:30:24,710
你是在开玩笑吧
You've got to be kidding me.

532
00:30:25,410 --> 00:30:27,410
他们没走多远吧
They didn't get very far, did they?

533
00:30:27,420 --> 00:30:28,660
谢谢
Thank you.

534
00:30:30,210 --> 00:30:31,120
还记得我们那位伙计
Remember our friend,

535
00:30:31,120 --> 00:30:33,730
那个被护送去机场的德国特工吗
The german agent and his escort to JFK?

536
00:30:33,730 --> 00:30:37,090
有个西装男在半路上
Apparently a guy in a suit shot them off the road

537
00:30:37,090 --> 00:30:39,200
用把大口径杀器把他们拦了下来
With a high-caliber weapon.

538
00:30:40,540 --> 00:30:41,940
我要去现场
I'm going to the scene,

539
00:30:42,020 --> 00:30:45,360
看看那家伙有没有留下关于科尔的线索
See if my guy left a trail that leads to Kohl.

540
00:30:52,930 --> 00:30:55,520
-我是弗斯科警探  -我要你帮忙
- Detective fusco. - I need your help.

541
00:30:55,600 --> 00:30:58,430
听好  先是他使唤我  现在你也来
Look... First him, now you.

542
00:30:58,430 --> 00:31:00,560
