Look, you guys just can't ring me up like I'm a bellhop.

543
00:31:00,570 --> 00:31:02,500
我们共同的朋友去追捕那个凶手了
Our mutual friend went after your perpetrator,

544
00:31:02,500 --> 00:31:04,490
而他好久没和我联系  肯定出事了
And I haven't heard from him-- something's wrong.

545
00:31:04,490 --> 00:31:07,010
那个男人比我们想的还要危险
This man may be more dangerous than we anticipated.

546
00:31:07,010 --> 00:31:07,770
我要你查一下...
I need you to check on--

547
00:31:07,770 --> 00:31:09,440
听着  我费了不少功夫让卡特相信
Look, I'm doing everything I can to convince Carter

548
00:31:09,440 --> 00:31:10,240
你家那位不是个麻烦
Your boy's not a problem.

549
00:31:10,240 --> 00:31:11,700
现在你又要让我的努力打水漂吗
Now you want me to just walk off the job?

550
00:31:11,700 --> 00:31:13,730
这就得你自己想办法解决了  事态紧急
Then you need to figure something out--it's urgent.

